Account Deletion Request
AI-Consigliere Daily Task
We respect your right to control your personal data. If you wish to delete your AI-Consigliere Daily Task account and all associated data, please follow the instructions below.

⚠️ Important: Account deletion is permanent and cannot be undone. All your tasks, preferences, and account data will be permanently removed from our systems.
How to Request Account Deletion
Option 1: In-App Deletion (Recommended)
Open the AI-Consigliere Daily Task app
Go to Settings
Scroll to Account Settings
Tap "Delete Account"
Confirm your decision
Your account will be deleted immediately
Option 2: Email Request
If you cannot access the app, send an email with the following information:

To: privacy@ai-consigliere.com
Subject: Account Deletion Request

Email Content:
I request the deletion of my AI-Consigliere Daily Task account and all associated data.

Account Email: [Your registered email address]
Reason for deletion: [Optional]

I understand this action is permanent and cannot be undone.

[Your Name]
What Gets Deleted
When you delete your account, we will permanently remove:

Your user profile and account information
All tasks, notes, and productivity data
App preferences and settings
Usage analytics associated with your account
Any backup data stored in our systems
Data Deletion Timeline
In-App Deletion: Immediate (within 24 hours)
Email Request: Within 30 days of receiving your request
Backup Systems: Completely removed within 90 days
Note: Some data may be retained for legal compliance purposes as outlined in our Privacy Policy, but it will be anonymized and not linked to your identity.
Before You Delete
Consider these alternatives:

Export Your Data: Download your tasks and data before deletion
Temporary Deactivation: Contact us about temporarily disabling your account
Privacy Settings: Adjust your privacy settings instead of full deletion
Need Help?
If you have questions about account deletion or need assistance:

Email: privacy@ai-consigliere.com

Response Time: Within 48 hours

Privacy Policy: View our Privacy Policy

